{"tid":1510890,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰城周三集會上訴　警方早前發出反對通知書","createTime":"2019-08-27T10:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T14:02:26.000Z","uid":66271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ea6ee9004940b15507f9b110112d782b586e363a","tid":1510890,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3208668/org/5118d927c8820fdedd159f591cd04936.jpg/rGJ6JXZ8SBlpuaFdBRrWpxxRkUhieYC2NQMikR8DIpE?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3208668%2Forg%2F5118d927c8820fdedd159f591cd04936.jpg%2FrGJ6JXZ8SBlpuaFdBRrWpxxRkUhieYC2NQMikR8DIpE%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=a831c820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《逃犯條例》引發連串示威，國泰航空疑因受壓，解僱多名曾參與示威或發表意見的員工，包括港龍工會主席施安娜。職工盟早前擬於周三（28日）在國泰城外發起集會，要求撤回解僱決定，捍衛言論自由，惟警方昨日（26曰）發出反對通知書，職工盟提出上訴。上訴委員會會議於今日下午5時30分舉行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3208677/org/119c8597a44f011d4e8ce1bcef951a54.jpg/m1XuVagGAhgvRDHrYucDp0IlZ46ldGPDspviJ5ib4ic?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3208677%2Forg%2F119c8597a44f011d4e8ce1bcef951a54.jpg%2Fm1XuVagGAhgvRDHrYucDp0IlZ46ldGPDspviJ5ib4ic%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=9ba38ec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n職工盟主席吳敏兒表示，就今次的上訴是否得直有一定信心，強調國泰方面要就解僱有關同事要有交代，並要有一個平台予相關同事解釋，並指這次是就近日社會活動而引申的首宗勞資糾紛，有別於近日的警民衝突，「警方唔應該將每星期因遊行活動之後嘅警民衝突入晒我哋數，根本兩件事，仲要係（因有關活動）首次嘅勞資問題。」<br />\n她強調現時未有結果，不會考慮任何後補計劃，一切留待及後決定。<br />\n<br />\n包圍國泰城集會最初訂於昨日，但由於警方口頭拒發出不反對通知書，職工盟決定將集會延至周三（28日）舉行，以爭取時間申請不反對通知書，惟至昨晚警方正式發出反對通知書，職工盟就此上訴。"},{"pid":"2374a9d8c17a6b16c1543fdad06d1effb9160f33","tid":1510890,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:51:05.000Z","msg":"照去 驚西"},{"pid":"e22f843a01139f380066097546a79a8b91b394c1","tid":1510890,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2374a9d8c17a6b16c1543fdad06d1effb9160f33","tid":1510890,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:51:05.000Z","msg":"照去 驚西"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有種國泰城開片<br />\n隨時移師機場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8c00a5d59edc10ca106cb78e470c41c60397d6","tid":1510890,"uid":255744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2374a9d8c17a6b16c1543fdad06d1effb9160f33","tid":1510890,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:51:05.000Z","msg":"照去 驚西"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:55:51.000Z","msg":"主辦單位可能有PlanB改地點。你去又係另外一回事"},{"pid":"ef8ed0e3a8396fa285b10f68ecddda432e63d797","tid":1510890,"uid":179729,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T11:22:22.000Z","msg":"國泰一定要撐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/epuPzvn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FepuPzvn.jpg&h=84d01f5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae887549b5baaee4c21796d387353f14f9756d01","tid":1510890,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:32:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1bdd01086f9f697d98543aa8650a16fb0627b8","tid":1510890,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f8c00a5d59edc10ca106cb78e470c41c60397d6","tid":1510890,"uid":255744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2374a9d8c17a6b16c1543fdad06d1effb9160f33","tid":1510890,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:51:05.000Z","msg":"照去 驚西"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:55:51.000Z","msg":"主辦單位可能有PlanB改地點。你去又係另外一回事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:46:19.000Z","msg":"蘋果岩岩報 聽日國泰城上訴失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n職工盟昨（26日）已提出另一集會申請，申請在明日（28日）下午4點至晚上7點，於中環愛丁堡廣場集會，呼籲員工及支持者勿浪費力氣時間到國泰城，應耐心等待職工盟宣佈愛丁堡集會是否獲批不反對通知書"},{"pid":"0a4df9c70a6bafbdba2a0f08dc9fb5ef97bdd9d9","tid":1510890,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a1bdd01086f9f697d98543aa8650a16fb0627b8","tid":1510890,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f8c00a5d59edc10ca106cb78e470c41c60397d6","tid":1510890,"uid":255744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2374a9d8c17a6b16c1543fdad06d1effb9160f33","tid":1510890,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:51:05.000Z","msg":"照去 驚西"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:55:51.000Z","msg":"主辦單位可能有PlanB改地點。你去又係另外一回事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:46:19.000Z","msg":"蘋果岩岩報 聽日國泰城上訴失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n職工盟昨（26日）已提出另一集會申請，申請在明日（28日）下午4點至晚上7點，於中環愛丁堡廣場集會，呼籲員工及支持者勿浪費力氣時間到國泰城，應耐心等待職工盟宣佈愛丁堡集會是否獲批不反對通知書"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:54:37.000Z","msg":"其實尋晚有報導去國泰城已經會出反對通知書，所以係改硬地點多。"},{"pid":"1be6d415e97837b7ed022006d95298fd400641ae","tid":1510890,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:00:57.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲扮乖仔跟足所謂規矩做野，只會比政府食硬。有guts就照舊於國泰城集會啦！改地點一係跪低，一係幫政權維穩"},{"pid":"2c091a94f81601e326d91cc6332ebd8b309c851b","tid":1510890,"uid":306180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:02:26.000Z","msg":"［文宣集合］人大831落閘五週年 香港人爭取雙真普選大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1510317\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1510317</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}